summary: This Series takes place after the events of HUGtto! Pretty Cure♡Futari wa Pretty Cure: All Stars Memories as it is establishing...
caption:
This Series takes place after the events of HUGtto! Pretty Cure♡Futari wa Pretty Cure: All Stars Memories as it is establishing the New Character Arc for the Pretty Cure Max Heart team, With Mepple and Mipple Explaining because of the Event’s of Having there Dreams and Future Destinies being obligated with the Destruction of the Land of Dreams and there Friends and families killed off because of Thanos Mass-Genocide… Nagisa Misumi and Honoka Yukishiro feel dissociated from there own human lives then being Pretty Cures, Like sometimes not eating with other people, Sometimes not attending School with a Fairy doing an announcement of there reasons, Having Out of Body Experiences while there Bodies are sleeping, but Ask yourselves, What do you think Having all your Dreams and futures forever gone and seeing all your Friends and Families turn into Dust does to a person?

When Two Scientific Minds coiled.
Now that the Nagisa and Honoka with the inclusion of Hikari Kujo are now staying on the Pokemon World with the Go Princess Pretty Cures, They make themselves home in Alola next to where the Three Ketchum boys are, So Nagisa can keep an eye on the Real Ash Ketchum for because Pretty Cure All Stars gave there Pieces of Heart to save his live, They not only Have Strong Feelings for him, But Nagisa is being a little bit over Protective.
At the Alola Pokemon School, Yana and Professor Kukui learn from Samson Oak that a new Junior Professor will be working with them… And… Much to Yana and Ash’s Shock and the joy of Haruka Haruno and Kirara Amanogawa… The New Junior Professor is Honoka, Yana wondered how is it possible with Honoka Holding a File of the Stuff she made back home with her Science friend, Like Creating Expanding Fibers, Self-Repairing Fibers, Rubberizing Liquid the list goes on, Impressing the Group, With Kirara to say that these are perfect for when the Girls want to give there Cure Soul’s a Break and let the Human Hosts do the Hero Work for a change, With Satoshi claiming It’s a Girls only thing while the Boys use Yana’s Gadgets, Yana while some Classes past with Honoka doing some teaching, Yana starts to feel like he’s knowledge has gotten outdated, With a hint of Jealousy, Which Mipple can sense, To They have a competition to see who is the smartest, While They are talking and Debating Mallow, Lana and Lillie do ask why Honoka is wearing White-tights in a Hot place like Alola, She does answer that they are part of one of her Experimental Nylon, That she and Nagisa are wearing and they involve the Expanding, and Cloaking Fibers, Honoka and Yana continue to there contest to see who is the Smartest and when they finish, Hybrid believes that Honoka and Yana have the same intelligence levels, Which impresses him, He wishes to study her mind more but then Team Skull causes trouble, With the Students dealing with them then Nagisa and Honoka face them, But they beat them without turning into Pretty Cures for that would be a waste of Pretty Cures energies, After wards Yana is proud to have Honoka be with the Alola School, Giving Ash and Satoshi the Chance to properly introduce Nagisa and Hikari to the entire school, With Kiawe and Sophocles wondering if the Pretty Cure team that started it all have come here, The rest might follow.

summary: (Joy@Darthoidan): Walking up to the ninetales hybrid, the vaporeon hybrid looked up with an excited smile on her face. "You look...
question: (Joy@Darthoidan): Walking up to the ninetales hybrid, the vaporeon hybrid looked up with an excited smile on her face. "You look like mythical god in a comic I read. Do you happen to be one?"
answer: The tall hybrid gazes his turquoise orbs downwards at the smaller creature. Viewing the spark of excitement, the pure joy shining from her face. He let out a hardy chuckle, amaze to see such enthusiasm. “I can assure you that I am no god.”, He responded with a confident tone. Though, not wanting to leave this young outsider with disappointment, he decided to state his next answer. “However… While I may not be a mythical god within your story, I am more than willing to use my illusionary ability to form into one, if you so wish.”

summary: My male Gardevoir, Ambrose, from my Alpha Sapphire. I have headcanon of him being blind and I wanted to give him a...
body:
My male Gardevoir, Ambrose, from my Alpha Sapphire. I have headcanon of him being blind and I wanted to give him a more…faerie-esque look, and I mean the wild half of things, not the graceful type we see more prevalent in modern media. He has antlers and horns, but for females, the horns aren’t as large. And while not pictured, he does have hooved feetsies. The fur is tattered and irregular for males, but females are a bit more orderly.

Oh, and he is blind. And a cocky little shit.
